attributes.text: Calculates the CREATE2 address for a fund without making any external calls
Estimate maximum possible amount of fund minted for amounts. Assumes correct order
Estimate minimum amounts needed to mint exact fund amount.
Sort token arrays to get the order used in the Controller and Fund.

params._tokenArray: The addresses that make the fund.
params.amounts: The amount of each token that we want to spend. Amounts should be in order.
params.deadline: The block timestamp where this transaction will expire.
params.fundMin: The min amount of IFT we expect to receive.
params.to: The address that receives the funds.

buyFundETH(address[],uint256[],uint256,a.details: The ethAmount should include UPPER slippage.

params._tokenArray: The addresses that make the fund.
params.amounts: Amounts of each token that the Helper will buy with the ETH/BNB. They should be in order.
params.deadline: The block timestamp where this transaction will expire.
params.fundAmount: The min amount of IFT we expect to receive.
params.to: The address that receives the funds.

params._tacoFactory: The amounts of the respective tokens that represent a (1) unit of the Fund Token
params._uniRouter: The DEX router used to trade tokens.

getAmountsInForETH(address,uint256).details: This is an expensive function if called from a transaction.

params.amountETH: The ETH amount that will be used in the transaction.

returns._0: The amounts for each token required.
returns._1: The exact ETH amount expected to be spent.

sellFund(address[],uint256,uint256[],add.details: amountsMin should include slippage of at least 0.001

params._tokenArray: The addresses that make the fund.
params.amountFund: Amount of fund token we wank to sell.
params.amountsMin: The min amount of tokens we expect to receive. Should be in order.
params.deadline: The block timestamp where this transaction will expire.
params.to: The address that receives the funds.

buyFund(address[],uint256,uint256[],addr.notice: Buys most funds possible using amounts given.

getAmountOut(address[],uint256[]).notice: Estimate maximum possible amount of fund minted for amounts. Assumes correct order

getAmountsInForETH(address,uint256).notice: Given ETH amount, estimate the min tokens amount[] to maximize fund acquisition.

sellFund(address[],uint256,uint256[],add.notice: Sells the fund token for underlying.

sortTokens(address[]).notice: Sort token arrays to get the order used in the Controller and Fund.
